}]]></script>

						  correlationId, step, requestorContext) {
	var rps = new sn_cmp_api.ResponseProcessorScript();
	var responseToProcess = rps.extractResponse(response);
	var responseObject = global.JSON.parse(responseToProcess);

	}

	return global.JSON.stringify(cloudModelObject);

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>sn_cmp.StorageVolumeRefQual</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>StorageVolumeRefQual</name><script><![CDATA[var StorageVolumeRefQual = Class.create();
StorageVolumeRefQual.prototype = {
	initialize: function() {
	},

	getAttachedVolumes: function(resourceId){

		var cmdbRelGR = new GlideRecord('cmdb_rel_ci');
		cmdbRelGR.addEncodedQuery("type="+this._getRelationshipSysIdFromType()+"^parent.sys_id="+resourceId+"^child.sys_class_name=cmdb_ci_endpoint_block");
		cmdbRelGR.query();
		var sysIdArr = [];
		while(cmdbRelGR.next()){
			sysIdArr.push(this._getVolumeIdFromBlockEndpoint(cmdbRelGR.getValue('child')));
		}

		return "sys_idIN" + sysIdArr.toString();
	},

	_getRelationshipSysIdFromType: function(){
		var cmdbRelTypeGR = new GlideRecord('cmdb_rel_type');
		cmdbRelTypeGR.addEncodedQuery('parent_descriptor=Use End Point To^child_descriptor=Use End Point From');
		cmdbRelTypeGR.setLimit(1);
		cmdbRelTypeGR.query();
		if (cmdbRelTypeGR.next()){
			return cmdbRelTypeGR.getValue('sys_id');
		}
	},

	_getVolumeIdFromBlockEndpoint: function(blockEndpointSysId){
		var blockEPGR = new GlideRecord('cmdb_ci_endpoint_block');
		blockEPGR.get(blockEndpointSysId);
		var volId = blockEPGR.getValue('object_id');

		var storageVolGR = new GlideRecord('cmdb_ci_storage_volume');
		storageVolGR.get('object_id', volId);
		return storageVolGR.getValue('sys_id');
	},

	type: 'StorageVolumeRefQual'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-10-01 08:34:33</sys_created_on><sys_id>dd252b5477580010c64450f79a1061fe</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>StorageVolumeRefQual</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Cloud Management Platform" source="sn_cmp">80d50579eb203200979aa5115206fedd</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Cloud Management Platform">80d50579eb203200979aa5115206fedd</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_dd252b5477580010c64450f79a1061fe</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-01 08:34:33</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update><sn_cmp_rp_filter action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE">
<name>getObjectIdByAvailabilityZone</name>
<resource_pool display_value="HardwareTypePool">6bd05230b70c3300d53b32c6ee11a964</resource_pool>
<script><![CDATA[getFilteredRecords(json);
//Do not remove function declaration
/** Input parameters
* @param json - map for properties which you need to run this script
* @returns filtered records in the format [{"value"="lookupValue",label="displayValue"}]
*/
function getFilteredRecords(json) {
    var filteredRecords = [];
    if (!gs.nil(json)) {
        var map = new global.JSON().decode(json);
        var availabilityZoneSysId = map.AvailabilityZone;
        if (!gs.nil(availabilityZoneSysId)) {
            var rel = new GlideRecord('cmdb_rel_ci');
            rel.addQuery('parent', availabilityZoneSysId);
            rel.addQuery('type.name', 'Contains::Contained by');
            rel.query();
            while (rel.next()) {
                var child = rel.getValue('child');
                var hardwareGr = new GlideRecord('cmdb_ci_compute_template');
                if (hardwareGr.get(child)) {
                    var relation = {};
                    relation.value = hardwareGr.getValue('object_id');
                    relation.label = hardwareGr.getValue('name');
                    filteredRecords.push(relation);
                }
            }
        }
    }
    //force to string
    return new global.JSON().encode(filteredRecords);
}]]></script>
